    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "Ablechroiulus spelaeus sp. n. and A. dudichi Andrássy, 1970 from Andalucía Oriental, Spain, with a discussion of the taxonomy of the genus Ablechroiulus Andrássy, 1966 (Nematoda, Rhabditida, Rhabditidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205410>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205411>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205413> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205410>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Ablechroiulus spelaeus sp. n. A: Neck region. B, F: Anterior region; C: Female, anterior genital branch. D: Female, entire. E: Male, entire. G: Female, caudal region. H: Male, caudal region." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205410/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205411>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ablechroiulus spelaeus sp. n. (LM). A: Neck region and detail of lip region showing setae. B: Female, caudal region. C: Male, caudal region and detail of spicule tip. Ablechroiulus dudichi Andrássy, 1970 (LM). D: Neck region and detail of lip region showing setae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205411/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205413>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Ablechroiulus dudichi Andrássy, 1970 (female). A: Neck region. B: Anterior region. C: Anterior genital branch and coelomocytes. D: Caudal region. E: Entire. F: Vulva (ventral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205413/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

